{"tid":772850,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟連登仔有無人性","createTime":"2018-08-09T05:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T07:09:59.000Z","uid":142433,"like":23,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"576872faf4a857ca3c64d5904054f40df290d28d","tid":772850,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:37:11.000Z","msg":"你地好恐怖<br />\n極端到成到網絡恐怖份子咁<br />\n可惜冇腦，俾幕後人利用緊都唔知<br />\n首先問一句，你地真係當左自己係判官，可以主宰別人生死?<br />\n好，咁你地落追殺令個陣，把刀係乜野，邊個幫你地班無能得把口9up既人做野?<br />\n仲睇唔到？咪傳媒囉<br />\n唔明白？你認為佢地咁好係只為左搵新聞就幫你地班廢柴？<br />\n做盲目道德白痴之前，諗下自己係咪真係咁偉大<br />\n你地失去既係言論自由，現實言論自由又好，網上言論自由又好<br />\n諗下而家香港咩環境，失去左就係永遠拎唔番<br />\n成個文革咁，不斷批鬥<br />\n個班乜撚報警白痴，不安白痴，做野之前咪唔經大腦囉<br />\n你要食花生咪去食，點解係要做埋d破壞言論自由自由既野？<br />\n講左d咩要自己負責番？<br />\n乜呢句咁似某警務人員講過既<br />\n唔係嘛高登人，你地咁快俾人洗腦？<br />\n炸迪迪尼個位男子，知唔知係衰咩呀，衰9up呀，<br />\n而家差佬唔洗上網搵人拉，因為有你地呢班傻仔幫佢，何樂而不為？<br />\n次次我都會講呢句<br />\n<br />\n言論自由就係你地呢班傻仔親手斷送，唔好怪人"},{"pid":"af95e73ac1f95fc78663f59916e92be9e145977c","tid":772850,"uid":166817,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:38:52.000Z","msg":"連登仔社會失敗者"},{"pid":"1ca5403dff73498fd87aaf18c30ff97fe642c836","tid":772850,"uid":142433,"like":21,"dislike":4,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:39:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/133945_8875698878ed1ccacfd5f6241116be90.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F133945_8875698878ed1ccacfd5f6241116be90.png&h=2fb9093f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0dfb463e3bfa4cc3793915cd46fa4c8d84d5351a","tid":772850,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:40:26.000Z","msg":"俾中共利用緊"},{"pid":"e19adde6b13f11a5f075494121bc8f8d0a40341e","tid":772850,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:42:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9819e2e42b7102d7acbde4efb64f6368095e976b","tid":772850,"uid":53498,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:42:09.000Z","msg":"同蝗接軌"},{"pid":"115da0d55e75d0ae3f4c7c8535569674cc0348d7","tid":772850,"uid":89514,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:43:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4263f1b29e4fb004696f82878ed40db15ca6421e","tid":772850,"uid":145923,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:43:25.000Z","msg":"失敗者的憤怒<br />\n一直作為一個失敗者<br />\n平常見他人生活美滿,唯自己落泊,只有一直懷恨於心<br />\n難得見人偶然有危機遇險.<br />\n即時自覺以為自己終於變成贏家<br />\n至身心興奮語無倫次."},{"pid":"6ae731259df4e507355be7ec59c2a16cea9468b5","tid":772850,"uid":37722,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:49:11.000Z","msg":"就咁睇呢個post, 完全唔知樓主講緊邊件事邊個post, 一味係度講情緒化言論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外樓主又將限制網上言論自由拉落連登仔口臭到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又想散播錯誤信息？"},{"pid":"6f405d971eeffd67005a8121b3ef661fcf57ce33","tid":772850,"uid":60764,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:55:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e0202aa3106612172896d14f3de44a202a0e542b","tid":772850,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6f405d971eeffd67005a8121b3ef661fcf57ce33","tid":772850,"uid":60764,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T05:55:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T06:05:05.000Z","msg":"連登仔都有好人 都會有惻隱之心"},{"pid":"adc41dff5b43e36b186adebd5f8294b98ff07872","tid":772850,"uid":9736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0202aa3106612172896d14f3de44a202a0e542b","tid":772850,"uid":142433,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6f405d971eeffd67005a8121b3ef661fcf57ce33","tid":772850,"uid":60764,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-0